<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It is a biography of a nation, region, a continent. It uses a non-fiction travel narrative to tell both the history and actuality of the Congo, Africa<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It is a biography of a nation, region, a continent. It uses a non-fiction travel narrative to tell both the history and actuality of the Congo, Africa's most turbulent nation, capturing a story that is shared with many other African nations.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
